channel.title: PooompScape V5
channel.description:
[center]Hey guys, This is it the moment you've been waiting for. PoompScape V5. It's still under construction and well, im going to ive you a preview of it. I got rid of Allstar because it got too old and it was full of shit which i didn't want and all that. This new server is a PI, with a few skills but i will be aiming to get every skill working. It has a Skill guide for what level the percific item needs, E.G Fishing you may need a Harpoon or a Lobster Cage, Farming you use the seeds on the patch to get the herb. Herblore works. [left]Features: - Really good server - Few skills working but will get all skills working - Thieving works by stealing from Stalls - D claws, Devine etc. - No second click trade, you just click talk to which is changed to Trade with - A NPC Selling stuff for all the skills - Client is Webclient ready - JAR ready - Old school runescape Background - Only one wave which is JAD - Ancients, Lunar etc - Good training spots - Varrock is PVP - Donator Zone - PK Shop - Name Changes E.G Shop Keeper is called Steve - KBD is not in Wild and is Multi - Fixed the PVP glitch when telling to Ardy - City teleports where you can sell stuff and just do what you want - Wilderness Works 100% - Perfect combat System - 10m Starter and when doing ::master or ::pure, you get items that are in that range.[/left]
Update Log: 95% of the skills works 100% Gnome agility course works 100% 95% Barb assault agility 100% Wilderness agility course Added Agility teleport to the Gnome agility
Things needed to do: Agility teleports and objects give XP Adding quests Adding a Minigame Make it Allstar look, but not allstar
There's some features that the server has. Here are some Pictures of the Server [img]http://i668.photobucket.com/albums/vv47/John5689/PoompScape/PoompScapeAncientcurse.gif[/img] [img]http://i668.photobucket.com/albums/vv47/John5689/PoompScape/StrengthCapeemote.gif[/img] [img]http://i668.photobucket.com/albums/vv47/John5689/PoompScape/Skilllookthrough.png[/img] [img]http://i668.photobucket.com/albums/vv47/John5689/PoompScape/RightClick.png[/img] [img]http://i668.photobucket.com/albums/vv47/John5689/PoompScape/PVPVarrock.png[/img] [img]http://i668.photobucket.com/albums/vv47/John5689/PoompScape/VarrockPK.png[/img] [img]http://i668.photobucket.com/albums/vv47/John5689/PoompScape/Monster.png[/img] [img]http://i668.photobucket.com/albums/vv47/John5689/PoompScape/Skills.png[/img] [img]http://i668.photobucket.com/albums/vv47/John5689/PoompScape/DonatorZone.png[/img] [img]http://i668.photobucket.com/albums/vv47/John5689/PoompScape/DonatorInterface.png[/img] [img]http://i668.photobucket.com/albums/vv47/John5689/PoompScape/Thieving.png[/img] [img]http://i668.photobucket.com/albums/vv47/John5689/PoompScape/Dclaws.gif[/img] Don't forget that this is only 10% of the server. There will be LOADS and i mean LOADS more thing added. like all the skills. Trying to make varrock a chill zone as well, and loads more. Flame as much as you like im not bothered really. I just had a hard time when i was in school and im 16 now and im heading to college doing ICT and maybe once that's done get into JAVA coding myself. Im still a novice by the way and well, it may look leeched but that's only a small amount of the server. Thank you and enjoy looking through it[/center]
